description:
Expressions       play alongside the pool : 在游泳池旁边玩耍。 &ldquo;do sth. alongside sw.&rdquo;
 Playing alongside the pool is dangerous. / It&rsquo;s dangerous playing alongside the pool. Charles will walk alongside the beach after giving performance tomorrow. (Charles 在明天演出完成后， 会在沙滩边散步。 N2L13) Don&rsquo;t drive alongside the road. (不要靠着路边开车)    Upside down: head is down and feet are up. stand on head (N2L6)
 作为 形容词 Percy Buttons asked for a meal and a glass of beer, in return for that, he kept upside down and sang songs.
